{"text_id":38228,"tokens":["In"," this"," paper",","," we"," investigate"," the"," orbital"," magnetization"," and"," its"," effects"," in"," spin","-","ch","iral"," ferro","magnetic"," Kag","ome"," lattice","."," Our"," study"," focuses"," on"," understanding"," the"," influence"," of"," the"," orbital"," magnetization"," on"," the"," electronic"," and"," magnetic"," properties"," of"," the"," Kag","ome"," lattice"," via"," the"," spin","-","orbit"," coupling","."," The"," Kag","ome"," lattice"," is"," a"," two","-","dimensional"," material"," composed"," of"," interconnected"," triangles",","," with"," the"," ability"," to"," exhibit"," exotic"," electronic"," states",".","We"," employ"," the"," tight","-","binding"," model"," and"," the"," Green","'","s"," function"," formalism"," to"," analyze"," the"," electronic"," band"," structures"," of"," the"," Kag","ome"," lattice","."," Our"," study"," revealed"," that"," the"," orbital"," magnetization"," leads"," to"," a"," shift"," in"," the"," electronic"," bands"," and"," the"," appearance"," of"," band"," gaps","."," The"," appearance"," of"," the"," gaps"," is"," attributed"," to"," the"," destruction"," of"," the"," chiral"," symmetry"," of"," the"," Kag","ome"," lattice"," due"," to"," the"," spin","-","orbit"," coupling","."," We"," also"," observed"," that"," the"," orbital"," magnetization"," has"," a"," significant"," effect"," on"," the"," electronic"," and"," magnetic"," properties"," of"," spin","-","ch","iral"," Kag","ome"," ferro","magnet","."," The"," applied"," magnetic"," field"," results"," in"," the"," changes"," of"," the"," magnetic"," moment",","," spin"," polarization",","," and"," the"," orbital"," angular"," momentum",".","Our"," research"," aims"," to"," provide"," a"," better"," understanding"," of"," the"," effects"," of"," the"," orbital"," magnetization"," in"," spin","-","ch","iral"," ferro","magnetic"," Kag","ome"," lattices","."," The"," study"," is"," motivated"," by"," the"," potential"," applications"," of"," these"," materials"," in"," next","-","generation"," electronic"," and"," magnetic"," devices","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}